      "text": "Last edit almost 5 years ago by svayambhu108\n\n96\nsaying something quite remarkable and unusual: world (identified by Schopenhauer with Brahman) turns out to be a dramatic story that can be rendered in words — although I saw it as reality, as reified, as substantia. Yes; this is what sub¬ stantia turns out to be, for me: not \"Deus sive natura sive substantia\" but \"Ultimate substance turns cut to be a dramatic story that shows up in print as a tracing, the underlying reality being a series of even",
